snippet.textDisplay: There should be songs for sons too, those who leave their homes to support their families. We often hear beautiful lyrics about daughters, and rightfully so, but sons also deserve that recognition. They miss home deeply, carry the same longing in their hearts, and yet often hide their tears, staying strong for the very people they ache for.
